txt.en: 'We know Dheghûn can be driven back to unknown. Find them, [placeholder]. Send them back.'
Rhûd-pulo-Drât now sees the Dheghûn as an even greater threat than the Orcs, and want you to defeat the mysterious beasts.
'They retreat? Very very good. Strong like Dhûrghud, you are.'
Dheghûn can be found throughout the Drúadan Forest.\n\nYou should defeat Dheghûn.
Rhûd-pulo-Drât can be found in Drû Bhûta.\n\nYou should speak with Rhûd-pulo-Drât.
